com/demo/doh/jarninface.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Eye of Zomm and Holgresh Beads</span><hr size=1> What really happened...<br><br>Monk kills Holgresh when Luclin comes out<br>Monk loots Holgresh Elder Beads, and notices that they can cast them from the general inventory slot.<br>Monk puts bead in bank since nobody will buy them.<br><br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Months later...</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br><br>Monk hears wizard complaining about spells again, but one spell they're complaining about is that eye spell on those beads.<br>Monk heads to graffes and see's that the reason we think Eye of Zohm is broken is because it's supposed to be a scouting spell, yet it gains aggro and dies from monsters. VI says that it's working as intended.<br>Monk goes to bank and gets his beads.<br>Monk heads to dungeon.<br>Monk learns to pull with eyes.<br>VI hears that Monks are pulling mobs with eyes, and not taking damage, so they decide to review Eye of Zohm.<br>After a few months of Monks paying 25-100kpp for Elder Holgresh Beads, VI decides to make the Eye a non-aggro NPC, similar to a Familiar.<br>Monks yell, scream, and cry that their toy has been nerfed.<br>Wizards yell, scream and cheer that their toy has been fixed.<br><br>Nerf or Fix? You decide!  <p><center><br><EMBED src="http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/jarninsig02.swf" quality=high loop=trueWIDTH=468 HEIGHT=80 TYPE="application/x-shockwave-flash"PLUGINSPAGE="http://www.macromedia.com/shockwave/download/index.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash"></EMBED></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/upeteltothemetel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Petel Tothemetel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/14/02 6:49:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboar